name: The Spiraliser Occasional Table
description: The Spiraliser Occasional Table forms part of the vibrant Wanderlust Collection and is a fun and charismatic example of modern British furniture design. This eye-catching design is ideal for those who want to inject a burst of colour and is available in a wide range of different shades to create different moods in high gloss and satin. These tables also look incredibly smart in any of Davidson's signature timber finishes. The table comes in a standard size specifically designed for use as the Spiraliser Occasional table. Bespoke sizes are also available upon request.
